class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="phillips-law" class="entry-website-title">Phillips Law</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-phillips-law-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-phillips-law-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-phillips-law-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Phillips Law"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://www.campstreetlaw.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://www.campstreetlaw.com
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>New Orleans, Louisiana, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Phillips Law is a Southern Louisiana law firm with experience across several practice areas, including criminal law, federal crimes, traffic violations, and personal injury. The firm's website features images of its lawyers and uses calm, professional shades of blue and sea green with crisp white, adding to a clean, sharp, and respectable image.</p><p>Key information regarding the firm, its practice areas, successes, client testimonials, contact details, and related resources are neatly and concisely laid out across several pages that are easily accessible from the site's top navigation menu.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>All essential information is easily found, and custom images and video make it personal and approachable. Prominent CTA buttons encourage visitors to contact the firm, and a dedicated testimonials page provides reassurance and credibility.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The site is missing a live chat feature. The website URL does not match the website name, which could be confusing. WAVE flagged multiple issues, inluding empty links and low contrast.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-phillips-law-20240522-desktop.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-phillips-law-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop home page welcomes visitors with a high-quality custom photo of the firm's attorneys, underscored by a contact button that is hard to miss. The top navigation menu is straightforward and legible, crowned by a CTA contact button for easy access.</p><p>Design elements and adequate spacing are consistent across the site's pages, with some pages featuring a convenient search function that contributes to a great user experience. On Google's PageSpeed Insights test, the desktop site achieved a performance score of 71/100.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-phillips-law-20240522-mobile.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-phillips-law-20240522-mobile.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The website adapts well to a mobile view, with images rendered in adequate sizes and other content suitably adjusted for easy reading and navigation from a hamburger menu in the top-right corner.</p><p>Contact information is also conspicuous, and some of the pages feature a convenient search box. The mobile site achieved a rather low performance score of 32/100 on Google's PageSpeed Insights test.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
class="entry-container entry-container-content"><div
class="entry-content-wrapper"><div
class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="trial-attorneys-texas" class="entry-website-title">Trial Attorneys Texas</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-trial-attorneys-texas-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-trial-attorneys-texas-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-trial-attorneys-texas-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Trial Attorneys Texas"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://trialattorneystexas.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://trialattorneystexas.com
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Dallas, Texas, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Trial Attorneys Texas is a legal firm for accident cases, medical malpractice, and nursing home negligence that serves clients throughout Texas. The site has a compelling theme and layout that includes a balanced use of text and visuals to provide comprehensive information about the firm, its practice areas, attorneys, results, and testimonials.</p><p>A clear navigation menu and the prominent placement of contact options contribute to its user-friendliness.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>A minimalistic design, concise navigation menu, and straightforward layout make the site easy to navigate. The site performed well on WAVE, with zero errors and just one alert flagging a redundant link.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The site could benefit from interactive features, such as live chat. Users may experience slower loading times on a mobile device.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-trial-attorneys-texas-20240522-desktop.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-trial-attorneys-texas-20240522-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The site works well on a desktop. The navigation menu and call-to-action buttons are neatly arranged and make it easy to access the different pages of the site, which display a consistent balance of text, images, and white space that aids readability. The desktop site achieved a performance score of 98/100 on Google's PageSpeed Insights test.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-trial-attorneys-texas-20240522-mobile.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-trial-attorneys-texas-20240522-mobile.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The site adjusts well to a mobile view and maintains adequate spacing for a good user experience. The menu and call-to-action buttons are displayed at the base of the screen rather than the top but are sufficiently conspicuous. On Google's PageSpeed Insights test, the mobile site achieved a performance score of 73/100.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
