class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="johnston-law-firm" class="entry-website-title">Johnston Law Firm</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-johnston-law-firm-20240524-desktop.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-johnston-law-firm-20240524-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-johnston-law-firm-20240524-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Johnston Law Firm"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://johnston-lawfirm.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://johnston-lawfirm.com
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Portland, Oregon, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Johnston Law Firm is a personal injury law firm based in Portland, Oregon. With a mission to make insurance companies and juries understand their clients' stories, the Johnston Law Firm represents clients in personal injury litigation, insurance denials, appeals, and other civil litigation matters.</p><p>The website lists all the firm's practice areas, along with their locations, client stories, and detailed attorney profiles accompanied by a list of awards, affiliations, past cases, and published works, demonstrating their experience and expertise. With regard to aesthetic elements, the site achieves a great balance between approachability, confidence, and legal prowess.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The use of the company logo and a consistent, matching color scheme across the site presents a strong brand identity. Contact buttons and a live chat feature facilitate easy user assistance. Client stories and testimonials present a trust factor.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The site is missing powerful, engaging visuals. WAVE flagged more than 40 low contrast errors, making the site less accessible for users with low vision.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-johnston-law-firm-20240524-desktop.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-johnston-law-firm-20240524-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop site features a well-spaced layout with prominent CTA buttons, including two for opening the live chat feature. The hero image is displayed clearly and appears professional, accompanied by a bold, catchy tagline promoting the firm's competencies. On Google's PageSpeed Insights test, the desktop site had an excellent performance score of 100/100.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-johnston-law-firm-20240524-mobile.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-johnston-law-firm-20240524-mobile.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The mobile site slims down adequately on smaller screens, maintaining the conspicuous CTA buttons, including both live chat buttons, a high-quality, confidence-instilling hero image, and the bold tagline promoting the firm.</p><p>However, its shortfall in comparison to the desktop version is its top CTA and hamburger menu buttons as they are not sticky. The mobile site scored 78/100 for performance on Google's PageSpeed Insights test.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
