width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop version is easy to navigate from a clear but rather packed top navigation menu. The "CALL NOW" button is clearly visible, as is the "Text us!" button toward the bottom-right of the home page.</p><p>While there is sufficient white space, copy-heavy pages can be overwhelming and would benefit from additional visual elements. The desktop site achieved a performance score of 88/100 on Google's PageSpeed Insights test.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
