src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The site could benefit from trust elements, such as client testimonials and past successes or case studies. WAVE flagged multiple issues, including a myriad of contrast errors, several skipped heading levels, and a few redundant links.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-cozza-law-group-20240522-desktop.webp"
