class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>Viewed on a desktop, the site's well-spaced layout and concise navigation menu make exploring and finding essential information easy. Call-to-action buttons stand out sufficiently, but the icon for the accessibility menu is rather small and easily overlooked. The desktop site achieved a performance score of 84/100 on Google's PageSpeed Insights test.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-websiteexample-cozza-law-group-20240522-mobile.webp"
